---
title: "_getAssetOutAmount (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_clamp_time: elapsedTime = min(elapsedTime, auctionDuration)
    q_clamp_time --> q_compute_multiplier: compute priceMultiplier via linear decay
    q_compute_multiplier --> q_get_out_price: multiplier = start - (start - end) * elapsed / duration
    q_get_out_price --> q_compute_usd: _getAssetPrice(assetOut, withValidation)
    q_compute_usd --> q_convert: auctionUsdValue = amountIn * assetInPrice / 10^decimals * multiplier
    q_convert --> [*]: return auctionUsdValue * 10^assetOutDecimals / assetOutPrice

    note right of q_compute_multiplier
        INV-001: priceMultiplier decays linearly from startingPriceMultiplier to endingPriceMultiplier
        INV-002: elapsedTime is clamped to auctionDuration (multiplier never goes below ending)
        INV-003: mulDivUp used for USD value and conversion (rounding favors protocol)
        INV-004: mulWadUp used for multiplier application (18-decimal fixed point)
    end note
